reviews.text: This food court is poor due to tables are NOT clean most the time. Seems like shortage of cleaner otherwise the cleaning rugs is dirty. Better bring yr own wipes. The roasted Duck wanton n rice poor attitude.  Taking wrong order n still scold vulgarity.  My first n last to patron the stall
